Some of the above classes are modified, as per cvs changelog for
these files - the original source code for these classes can be
downloaded from the PEAR project site, at http://pear.php.net/.
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Smarty:

wCMS also makes use of, and is distributed with, Smarty. Smarty is
released under the LGPL. Some parts of the code are changed, and
some files removed, to reduce overheads, the original source code
can be downloaded from http://smarty.php.net
--------------------------------------------------------------------

All these files have their original copyright statements intact. All
Smarty related files are located in the smarty directory, and all PEAR
classes are located in the pear directory.